  "vulnerable": true,
  "cwe": "CWE-22",
  "location": "validatePath function",
  "explanation": "The code is vulnerable to directory traversal because the validatePath function only checks if the beginning of the constructed path matches the public root, but it does not prevent the use of '..' or other path manipulation techniques to escape the intended directory."
